data.description: Commuter's Dream! This property is located in Temple Hills, MD within 5 miles from DC Line. Easy access to 495 and Suitland Parkway and Metro. This 3 bedroom 2 Full bath brick rambler is great investment property or starter home. Property has updated stainless steel appliances, a large outdoor deck with access to a huge back yard.  Home offers both on street and off street parking with enough space for up to 3 cars and back yard access. Basement has a large family room, a bonus room that can be used as an office or den with closet space.  Basement also has ample storage space, a full laundry room and an updated full bath with a walk- in shower. Property is sold AS-IS.
